all_users_one_ref_guard.name: all_users_one_ref_guard
all_users_one_ref_guard.where:
(CASE WHEN "all_user"."user_id" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END +
                   CASE WHEN "all_user"."temporary_user_id" IS NOT NULL THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) = 1

memory_assets_dimensions_positive.name: memory_assets_dimensions_positive
memory_assets_dimensions_positive.value: ("memory_assets"."width" IS NULL OR "memory_assets"."width" > 0) AND ("memory_assets"."height" IS NULL OR "memory_assets"."height" > 0)
